Using nested array notation for uploads


It is suggested that you always use the 
Zend\Http\PhpEnvironment\Request

object to retrieve and merge the 
$_FILES
 information with the form, instead
of using 
$_FILES
 directly,  due to how the file information is
mapped in the 
$_FILES
 array:


